Package de.flyndre.fleventsbackend.services

Klasse FleventsAccountService

java.lang.Object
de.flyndre.fleventsbackend.services.FleventsAccountService
@Service public class FleventsAccountService extends Object
This Service provides usage and logic for the FleventsAccount repository. It provides methods for manipulating the data of these repositories.
Autor:
Paul Lehmann

    • validate

      public FleventsAccount validate(String email, String secret)
      Checks whether the secret matches the email. Throws an Exception if the mail does not exist or if the given secret is not matching the mail.
      Parameter:
      email - the email of the account to validate
      secret - the secret to validate
      Gibt zurück:
      FleventsAccount linked to the given mail if the secret is correct

    • getAccountByMail

    • createAccount

      public FleventsAccount createAccount(FleventsAccount account)
      Creates the given account in the database. Throws an Exception if the given account is invalid or if the email is already in use.
      Parameter:
      account - the account to be saved
      Gibt zurück:
      FleventsAccount the saved account

    • createAnonymousAccount

      public FleventsAccount createAnonymousAccount(String email)

      Parameter:
      email - the email for the account to be created
      Gibt zurück:
      FleventsAccount which has been created
